#: .\0_spells.json
msgid "...monster spell. Fear"
msgstr "...怪物法术。恐惧"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '...monster spell. Fear'}
#: .\0_spells.json
msgid "Scare the crap out of humans."
msgstr "把人类吓得屁滚尿流。"

#: .\0_spells.json
msgid "...monster spell. Stress"
msgstr "...怪物法术。压力"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '...monster spell. Stress'}
#: .\0_spells.json
msgid "Drive people stupid."
msgstr "把人逼疯。"

#: .\0_spells.json
msgid "...monster spell. Feedback"
msgstr "...怪物法术。反馈"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '...monster spell. Feedback'}
#: .\0_spells.json
msgid "Cause Psychic Feedback to humans."
msgstr "对人类造成精神反馈。"

#: .\0_spells.json
msgid "...monster spell. Flaming eye stare"
msgstr "...怪物法术。火焰之眼凝视"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '...monster spell. Flaming eye stare'}
#: .\0_spells.json
msgid "Feedback + Daze"
msgstr "反馈 + 眩晕"

#: .\0_spells.json
msgid "...monster spell. Madness"
msgstr "...怪物法术。疯狂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '...monster spell. Madness'}
#: .\0_spells.json
msgid "Permanent crazy."
msgstr "永久疯狂。"

#: .\0_spells.json
msgid "Psychic Fortress"
msgstr "精神堡垒"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Psychic Fortress'}
#: .\0_spells.json
msgid ""
"A mental shield to resist psychic attacks.  Erects a towering fortress of "
"encouraging memories and benevolvent images around the human psyche."
msgstr "一种抵抗精神攻击的精神护盾。在人类心灵周围建立起一座由鼓舞人心的记忆和仁慈意象构成的高耸堡垒。"

#: .\0_spells.json
msgid "Encage Instincts"
msgstr "禁锢本能"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Encage Instincts'}
#: .\0_spells.json
msgid ""
"A mental shield to resist fear.  Captures one's own instincts of self-"
"preservation in a shimmering cage of pure will, disallowing natural fears to"
" overpower the ego."
msgstr "一种抵抗恐惧的精神护盾。将自我保存的本能捕获在一个由纯粹意志构成的闪烁牢笼中，防止自然恐惧压倒自我。"

#: .\0_spells.json
msgid "Enforced Duality"
msgstr "强制二元性"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Enforced Duality'}
#: .\0_spells.json
msgid ""
"A mental shield to resist damaging psychic attacks.  Strenthens the duality "
"of the mind and body by sealing chakras and preventing attacks on the brain-"
"stem that cause psychosomatic reactions."
msgstr "一种抵抗有害精神攻击的精神护盾。通过封闭脉轮并防止对脑干的攻击（这些攻击会导致心身反应），来强化心灵与肉体的二元性。"

#: .\0_spells.json
msgid "Inverse Microcosm"
msgstr "逆反微观世界"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Inverse Microcosm'}
#: .\0_spells.json
msgid ""
"A short-term shield to block all psychic attacks.  Transforms the psyche "
"into a self-sustaining microcosm, cut off from outside influences."
msgstr "一种阻挡所有精神攻击的短期护盾。将心灵转化为一个自我维持的微观世界，切断外部影响。"

#: .\0_spells.json
msgid "...item spell. remove madness."
msgstr "...物品法术。移除疯狂。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '...item spell. remove madness.'}
#: .\0_spells.json
msgid "A meditation to heal lasting psychic traumas."
msgstr "一种治愈持久精神创伤的冥想。"

#: .\0_spells.json
msgid "Amplifying Mandala"
msgstr "增幅曼荼罗"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Amplifying Mandala'}
#: .\0_spells.json
msgid ""
"Temporarily boosts Intelligence and Perception.  You form a spinning mandala"
" of light in your mind's eye, allowing you to alter neural pathways with "
"greater efficiency."
msgstr "暂时提升智力和感知。你在心灵之眼中形成一个旋转的光之曼荼罗，让你能更高效地改变神经通路。"

#: .\0_spells.json
msgid "Neural Delimiter"
msgstr "神经定界器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Neural Delimiter'}
#: .\0_spells.json
msgid ""
"Temporarily boosts Speed.  Removes neural limits and conditioned inhibitors "
"to momentarily increase mental speed."
msgstr "暂时提升速度。移除神经限制和条件性抑制剂，以暂时提高思维速度。"

#: .\0_spells.json
msgid "reduce fear "
msgstr "减少恐惧"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'reduce fear '}
#. ~ Description for {'str': '...bionic spell. psychic shield'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': '...bionic spell. feedback'}
#: .\0_spells.json .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#: .\0_spells.json
msgid "...bionic spell. psychic shield"
msgstr "...仿生法术。精神护盾"

#: .\0_spells.json
msgid "...bionic spell. feedback"
msgstr "...仿生法术。反馈"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "[ NPC,THRALL ] Submit!"
msgstr "[ NPC,THRALL ] 臣服！"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "[MESMERISM] Look into my eyes, friend."
msgstr "[催眠术] 看着我的眼睛，朋友。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "I feel... sleepy... all of a sudden."
msgstr "我感觉……突然……好困……"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "You were saying something earlier?"
msgstr "你刚才说了什么吗？"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "[vs PER+INT] Your mind is too weak to resist me."
msgstr "[对抗 感知+智力] 你的意志太薄弱，无法抵抗我。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "[vs TRAITS] Your mind is fragile and unbalanced."
msgstr "[对抗 特质] 你的心灵脆弱且失衡。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "Yes.  Sleepy.  Very sleepy..."
msgstr "是的。困了。非常困……"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "Your eyes are tired.  Your mind is wrapped in thick fog."
msgstr "你的眼睛很疲惫。你的思绪被浓雾笼罩。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "Wha!  What was that?  I zoned out for a second."
msgstr "哇！那是什么？我刚才走神了一下。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "So tired..."
msgstr "好累……"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid ""
"From henceforth, you will be my psychic thrall, forever bound to my will! "
"(only one attempt per NPC)"
msgstr "从今往后，你将成为我的灵能奴仆，永远受我意志束缚！（每个NPC仅限尝试一次）"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "Set down your weapon.  There is no need for violence."
msgstr "放下你的武器。没有必要使用暴力。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid ""
"We should travel together as companions.  Doesn't that sound like a good "
"idea?  A good idea."
msgstr "我们应该结伴同行。这听起来不是个好主意吗？一个好主意。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid ""
"[NPC -ANGER]  Let go of your hostility and relax.  Relax.  Be peaceful and "
"serene."
msgstr "[NPC -ANGER] 放下你的敌意，放松。放松。保持平和与宁静。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid ""
"[NPC +TRUST]  You must trust me more.  Trust me.  We're the best of friends,"
" you and I.  Friends."
msgstr "[NPC +TRUST] 你必须更加信任我。信任我。我们是最好的朋友，你和我。朋友。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid ""
"[NPC -FEAR]  Do not fear for your safety.  Safety.  We're perfectly safe."
msgstr "[NPC -FEAR] 不要担心你的安全。安全。我们非常安全。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid ""
"[NPC +SLEEP]  Yes sleep.  Let the heaviness pull you into a deep slumber.  "
"Sleep."
msgstr "[NPC +SLEEP] 是的，睡吧。让沉重感将你拖入深沉的睡眠。睡吧。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "You will forget all about this..."
msgstr "你会忘记这一切……"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "I hear and obey."
msgstr "我听从并服从。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "Purge yourself of weakness and evil, minion!"
msgstr "清除你自身的软弱与邪恶吧，仆从！"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid ""
"Fortify your mind to the horrors of the cosmos.  Many dangers lie ahead."
msgstr "让你的心智对宇宙的恐怖坚不可摧。前方危险重重。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "Let go of your pain."
msgstr "放下你的痛苦。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "[NPC +VALUE]  Submit your will to me."
msgstr "[NPC +VALUE] 将你的意志交给我。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "Lend me your life-power, mindslave."
msgstr "将你的生命力借给我，心智奴隶。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid ""
"You have picked the wrong target, 'friend', for I too am awakened to the powers of the mind.  \n"
"Prepare yourself for battle!"
msgstr ""
"你选错了目标，“朋友”，因为我也已觉醒了心灵之力。\n"
"准备战斗吧！"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "Forgive my mistake! I concede..."
msgstr "原谅我的错误！我认输……"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "Another psychic?  So be it.  Let the duel begin!"
msgstr "又一个灵能者？那就这样吧。让决斗开始！"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "How does a duel work?"
msgstr "决斗如何进行？"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid ""
"A psychic duel is fought in a series of rounds.  \n"
"Each successful round establishes one 'contact'.  \n"
"The first to gain three contacts wins.  \n"
"You can also risk an assault with less than three contacts,  \n"
" but a failed assault results in instant defeat."
msgstr ""
"灵能决斗以一系列回合进行。\n"
"每个成功的回合建立一个“连接”。\n"
"首先获得三个连接者获胜。\n"
"你也可以在少于三个连接时冒险发动攻击，\n"
"但攻击失败会导致立即战败。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "I see..."
msgstr "我明白了……"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "<mesmer_0c>"
msgstr "<mesmer_0c>"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "* DUEL * [0/3]"
msgstr "* 决斗 * [0/3]"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "* CONCEDE *"
msgstr "* 认输 *"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "<mesmer_1c>"
msgstr "<mesmer_1c>"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "* DUEL * [1/3]"
msgstr "* 决斗 * [1/3]"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "* Final Assault *"
msgstr "* 最终攻击 *"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "<mesmer_2c>"
msgstr "<mesmer_2c>"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "* DUEL * [2/3]"
msgstr "* 对决 * [2/3]"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "Ha ha.  Your defenses are crumbling.  [1/3]"
msgstr "哈哈。你的防御正在崩溃。[1/3]"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "You'll never defeat me.  [2/3]"
msgstr "你永远无法击败我。[2/3]"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "It's not over yet."
msgstr "还没结束呢。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "Just you wait."
msgstr "等着瞧吧。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "We'll see about that."
msgstr "我们走着瞧。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid ""
"[+INSOMNIA] * Absorb your opponent's sleep disorder, permanently, to gain "
"one contact."
msgstr "[+失眠症] * 永久吸收对手的睡眠障碍，以获得一个联系人。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid ""
"[-ANIMAL EMPATHY] * Sacrifice your empathic nature, permanently, to remove "
"two of your opponent's contacts."
msgstr "[-动物共情] * 永久牺牲你的共情天性，以移除对手的两个联系人。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid ""
"[+SCHIZO +MOODSWINGS] * Damage your mental state, permanently, to remove two"
" of your opponent's contacts."
msgstr "[+精神分裂症 +情绪波动] * 永久损害你的精神状态，以移除对手的两个联系人。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid ""
"[TERRIFYING vs JITTERY] * Leverage your terrifying nature to gain one "
"contact and remove one of your opponent's."
msgstr "[恐怖 vs 紧张不安] * 利用你恐怖的天性，获得一个联系人并移除对手的一个联系人。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid ""
"[vs SQUEAMISH] * Take advantage of your opponent's neurosis to gain one "
"contact.  This will cause you psychic feedback."
msgstr "[vs 神经质] * 利用对手的神经症获得一个联系人。这会导致你精神反噬。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid ""
"[SPIRITUAL] * Rely on your spirituality to remove one of your opponent's "
"contacts.  This will also summon dark beings from your subconscious mind."
msgstr "[灵性] * 依靠你的灵性移除对手的一个联系人。这也会从你的潜意识中召唤黑暗存在。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid ""
"[+PACIFIST] Destroy your inner hostility, permanently, to remove two of your"
" opponent's contacts."
msgstr "[+和平主义者] 永久摧毁你内心的敌意，以移除对手的两个联系人。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "No!  Defeated?  How can this be?"
msgstr "不！被打败了？这怎么可能？"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid ""
"I have proven myself to be the superior mentalist.  \n"
"There is no need to punish you for your inevitable failure."
msgstr ""
"我已证明自己是更优越的心灵术士。\n"
"无需因你必然的失败而惩罚你。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "You have failed.  Now fall into a deep slumber."
msgstr "你失败了。现在陷入沉睡吧。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid ""
"You are too dangerous to let go. \n"
"I will crush your mind and seal your powers."
msgstr ""
"你太危险，不能放过。\n"
"我将碾碎你的心智，封印你的力量。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid ""
"Those who oppose me...  \n"
"...must DIE!"
msgstr ""
"与我为敌者……\n"
"……必死无疑！"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "Ha ha!  Pathetic.  You stood no chance against my highly evolved mind."
msgstr "哈哈！可悲。你根本不是我高度进化心智的对手。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "So this is how it ends..."
msgstr "这就是结局吗……"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "What a humiliating defeat."
msgstr "多么耻辱的失败。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "Mercy!"
msgstr "饶命！"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid ""
"A wise choice.  There is no doubt your frail mind would be crushed under the"
" weight of my awesome power."
msgstr "明智的选择。毫无疑问，你脆弱的心智会被我强大力量的重压碾碎。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "Someday..."
msgstr "总有一天……"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "Yes?  They're... uh... very nice."
msgstr "是吗？它们……呃……非常不错。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "Damn!"
msgstr "该死！"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "So... tired..."
msgstr "好……困……"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "Awaken.  And forget this ever happened."
msgstr "醒来吧。然后忘记这一切。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "Yes sleep.  Let the heaviness pull you into a deep slumber.  Sleep!"
msgstr "是的，睡吧。让沉重感将你拖入深沉的睡眠。睡吧！"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "[MESMER]  There is no item.  You must be seeing things."
msgstr "[催眠] 没有物品。你一定是眼花了。"

#: .\TALK_MESMER.json
msgid "I must be seeing things."
msgstr "我一定是眼花了。"

#: .\ammo_types.json
msgid "psychic"
msgstr "灵能者"

#: .\bionics.json
msgid "Bionic Lobotomy Kit"
msgstr "仿生脑白质切除工具包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bionic Lobotomy Kit'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bionic Lobotomy CBM'}
#: .\bionics.json .\items.json
msgid ""
"Microrobots programmed to sever malfunctioning neural pathways and balance "
"neuro-chemicals."
msgstr "编程用于切断故障神经通路并平衡神经化学物质的微型机器人。"

#: .\bionics.json
msgid "Prototype Fear Reducer"
msgstr "原型恐惧抑制器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Prototype Fear Reducer'}
#: .\bionics.json
msgid ""
"Your brain has been equipped with a microcomputer capable of releasing "
"targeted chemical suppressors.  This makes you resistant to the overwhelming"
" fear of extradimensional creatures.  Activate it to triiger the effect."
msgstr "你的大脑已装备了一台能够释放针对性化学抑制剂的微型计算机。这使你能够抵抗来自异次元生物的压倒性恐惧。激活它以触发效果。"

#: .\bionics.json
msgid "Prototype Mind Shield"
msgstr "原型心灵护盾"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Prototype Mind Shield'}
#: .\bionics.json
msgid ""
"Your skull has been equipped with a mesh of charged nano-fibers which allow "
"you to better resist psychic attacks.  Activate it to triiger the effect"
msgstr "你的头骨已装备了一层带电纳米纤维网，使你能够更好地抵抗灵能攻击。激活它以触发效果。"

#: .\classes.json .\mutations.json
msgid "Mesmerist"
msgstr "催眠师"

#: .\classes.json
msgid "I wander the hidden pathways of the cosmos."
msgstr "我漫步于宇宙的隐秘小径。"

#: .\classes.json
msgid "Beggar"
msgstr "乞丐"

#: .\classes.json
msgid "I'm just trying to survive."
msgstr "我只是想活下去。"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Dazed"
msgstr "眩晕"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Dazed'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"You're visibly shaken up, and are having a hard time focusing on what's "
"going on around you."
msgstr "你明显受到了惊吓，难以集中注意力观察周围的情况。"

#. ~ Apply message for effect(s) 'Dazed'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "You are dazed!"
msgstr "你感到眩晕！"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Nervous"
msgstr "紧张"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Afraid"
msgstr "害怕"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Terrified"
msgstr "恐惧"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Abject Horror"
msgstr "极度恐惧"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Abject Horror!"
msgstr "极度恐惧！"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Abject Horror!!"
msgstr "极度恐惧！！"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Abject Horror!!!"
msgstr "极度恐惧！！！"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Your soul is gripped with a paralytic fear."
msgstr "你的灵魂被一种麻痹性的恐惧所攫取。"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "You bravely attempt to resist the fear."
msgstr "你勇敢地试图抵抗恐惧。"

#. ~ Apply message for effect(s) 'Nervous, Nervous, Nervous, Nervous, Afraid,
#. Afraid, Afraid, Afraid, Terrified, Terrified, Terrified, Terrified, Abject
#. Horror, Abject Horror!, Abject Horror!!, Abject Horror!!!'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "You have been gripped with fear."
msgstr "你已被恐惧所攫取。"

#. ~ Remove message for effect(s) 'Nervous, Nervous, Nervous, Nervous, Afraid,
#. Afraid, Afraid, Afraid, Terrified, Terrified, Terrified, Terrified, Abject
#. Horror, Abject Horror!, Abject Horror!!, Abject Horror!!!'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "The fear subsides."
msgstr "恐惧逐渐消退。"

#. ~ Miss message for effect(s) 'Nervous, Nervous, Nervous, Nervous, Afraid,
#. Afraid, Afraid, Afraid, Terrified, Terrified, Terrified, Terrified, Abject
#. Horror, Abject Horror!, Abject Horror!!, Abject Horror!!!'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "Other worldly fear washes over you."
msgstr "来自异界的恐惧席卷了你。"

#. ~ Miss message for effect(s) 'Nervous, Nervous, Nervous, Nervous, Afraid,
#. Afraid, Afraid, Afraid, Terrified, Terrified, Terrified, Terrified, Abject
#. Horror, Abject Horror!, Abject Horror!!, Abject Horror!!!'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "Alien dread fills your soul"
msgstr "异样的恐惧充满了你的灵魂。"

#. ~ Miss message for effect(s) 'Nervous, Nervous, Nervous, Nervous, Afraid,
#. Afraid, Afraid, Afraid, Terrified, Terrified, Terrified, Terrified, Abject
#. Horror, Abject Horror!, Abject Horror!!, Abject Horror!!!'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "Indescribable terror knaws at your consciousness."
msgstr "难以言喻的恐怖啃噬着你的意识。"

#. ~ Miss message for effect(s) 'Nervous, Nervous, Nervous, Nervous, Afraid,
#. Afraid, Afraid, Afraid, Terrified, Terrified, Terrified, Terrified, Abject
#. Horror, Abject Horror!, Abject Horror!!, Abject Horror!!!'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "The fear is overhwelming."
msgstr "恐惧令人难以承受。"

#. ~ Miss message for effect(s) 'Nervous, Nervous, Nervous, Nervous, Afraid,
#. Afraid, Afraid, Afraid, Terrified, Terrified, Terrified, Terrified, Abject
#. Horror, Abject Horror!, Abject Horror!!, Abject Horror!!!'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "\"You need to get out of here.\""
msgstr "\"你得离开这里。\""

#. ~ Miss message for effect(s) 'Nervous, Nervous, Nervous, Nervous, Afraid,
#. Afraid, Afraid, Afraid, Terrified, Terrified, Terrified, Terrified, Abject
#. Horror, Abject Horror!, Abject Horror!!, Abject Horror!!!'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "\"Run Away.\""
