#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Awakened"
msgstr "觉醒"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Awakened'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"You have awakened to the dark realities of psychic phenomena and to the "
"invisible forces that stream through the cosmos."
msgstr "你已觉醒，洞悉了灵能现象的黑暗现实，以及那流经宇宙的无形之力。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Fearless"
msgstr "无所畏惧"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Fearless'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"You fear nothing, at least from planet Earth.  You are also somewhat "
"resistant to cosmic horrors and fear-based psychic attacks.  However, this "
"also prevents you from ever gaining psychic powers."
msgstr "你无所畏惧，至少对地球上的事物如此。你对宇宙恐怖和基于恐惧的灵能攻击也有一定抵抗力。然而，这也使你永远无法获得灵能力量。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Willpower"
msgstr "意志力"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Willpower'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"You have an indomitable will, and are resistant to psychic attacks.  "
"However, this also prevents you from ever gaining psychic powers."
msgstr "你拥有不屈的意志，并能抵抗灵能攻击。然而，这也使你永远无法获得灵能力量。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Fear Resistant"
msgstr "恐惧抵抗"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Fear Resistant'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"You have evolved past your primitive fight-or-flight instincts.  Penalties "
"for fear are reduced."
msgstr "你已进化，超越了原始的“战或逃”本能。恐惧带来的惩罚效果有所减轻。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Mesmerist'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Through strength of personality, you can persuade and entrance the weak "
"willed."
msgstr "凭借强大的人格力量，你可以说服并迷惑意志薄弱者。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Psychic Defense"
msgstr "灵能防御"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Psychic Defense'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your overly sensitive mind has adapted to constant psychic stress.  You can "
"now actively defend yourself against fear and psychic onslaughts."
msgstr "你那过度敏感的心智已适应了持续的灵能压力。你现在可以主动防御恐惧与灵能冲击。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Psychic Projection"
msgstr "灵能投射"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Psychic Projection'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your expanding mind has begun to reach beyond the borders of your physical "
"self.  You can now materialize objects and infuse them with your power."
msgstr "你不断扩展的心智已开始超越肉体自我的边界。你现在可以将物体具象化，并为其灌注你的力量。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "You concentrate your psychic energies into material form"
msgstr "你将灵能集中，使其化为物质形态"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Psychic Strength"
msgstr "灵能强度"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Psychic Strength'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your growing consciousness has subsumed portions of your autonomous nervous "
"system.  You have gained the power to temporarily overcome physical limits."
msgstr "你不断增长的意识已接管了部分自主神经系统。你获得了暂时突破生理极限的力量。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Enthralled"
msgstr "被迷惑"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Enthralled'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid "This person has been overcome by your mesmeric powers."
msgstr "此人已被你的催眠力量所征服。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Unthrall"
msgstr "解除迷惑"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Unthrall'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid "This person is now immune to enthralling."
msgstr "此人现在对迷惑效果免疫。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Lobotomized"
msgstr "脑叶切除"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Lobotomized'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Either through surgery or purely psychic means, you have had your psychic "
"powers removed."
msgstr "无论是通过外科手术还是纯粹的灵能手段，你的灵能力量已被移除。"

#: .\mutations_override.json
msgid "Optimist"
msgstr "乐观主义者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Optimist'}
#: .\mutations_override.json
msgid ""
"Nothing gets you down!  You savor the joys of life, ignore its hardships, "
"and are generally happier than most people."
msgstr "没有什么能让你消沉！你品味生活的乐趣，无视其中的艰辛，总体上比大多数人更快乐。"

#: .\mutations_override.json
msgid "Schizophrenic"
msgstr "精神分裂症"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Schizophrenic'}
#: .\mutations_override.json
msgid ""
"You will periodically suffer from delusions, ranging from minor effects to "
"full visual hallucinations.  Some of these effects may be controlled through"
" the use of Thorazine."
msgstr "你会周期性地遭受妄想困扰，从轻微影响到完全的视觉幻觉不等。其中一些效果可以通过使用氯丙嗪来控制。"

#: .\mutations_override.json
msgid "Jittery"
msgstr "紧张不安"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Jittery'}
#: .\mutations_override.json
msgid ""
"During moments of great stress or under the effects of stimulants, you may "
"find your hands shaking uncontrollably, severely reducing your Dexterity."
msgstr "在承受巨大压力或受兴奋剂影响时，你可能会发现双手不受控制地颤抖，严重降低你的敏捷属性。"

#: .\professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Awakened"
msgstr "觉醒"

#: .\professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Awakened"
msgstr "觉醒"

#. ~ Profession (male Awakened) description
#: .\professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You've always been eccentric, maybe even a bit crazy.  But now that the "
"whole world has gone crazy and reality is turning itself inside out, your "
"mind has begun to awaken to the awful truths and dark mysteries of the "
"cosmos."
msgstr "你一直都很古怪，甚至可能有点疯狂。但如今整个世界都已陷入疯狂，现实正被彻底颠覆，你的心智已开始觉醒，直面宇宙那骇人的真相与黑暗的奥秘。"

#. ~ Profession (female Awakened) description
#: .\professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
